<div>
<p><img loading="lazy" width="250" height="184" border="0" align="right" title="run" alt="run" src="//farm3.static.flickr.com/2211/2117551560_878e603bee_o.jpg" />December 15, 1927&nbsp;</p>
<p>Miss Grace Shannon, national secretary of our own YWCA, has just returned from Turkey, and good news:&nbsp; there&rsquo;s no Dumb Doras there!&nbsp; Sure, it&rsquo;s all right for a man to have four wives (&ldquo;to which every good Mussulman says &lsquo;Amen,&rsquo;&rdquo; chuckles Ms. Shannon), but the crafty gals there under Atat&uuml;rk (we say atagirl!) have found some loophole that goes on to contradict such (referring to the famous Koranic<em> Koran 4:3/Koran 4:129 Paradox</em>).&nbsp; Yes, it seems the <a title="ataboy" target="_blank" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mustafa_Kemal_Atat%C3%BCrk">new republic</a>&rsquo;s progressive divorce laws and campaigns for women&rsquo;s sufferage have made it a veritable heaven on earth for the gentler gender. &nbsp;</p>
<p>Just think, another eighty years of progressive thinking will do a world of <a title="youdontsay" target="_blank" href="http://humanrights.tribe.net/thread/54d72d19-b458-462c-9725-f9c79036e8a9">wonder</a> for <a title="themoderns" target="_blank" href="http://www.nytimes.com/2005/12/04/magazine/04berlin.html?_r=3&#038;pagewanted=2&#038;oref=slogin&#038;oref=slogin&#038;oref=slogin">women</a>!</p>
</div>
